        {
          "title": "Modifying HSLA",
          "level": 3,
          "cards": [
            {
              "title": "Modifying HSLA",
              "body": "```scss\ndarken($color, 5%)\nlighten($color, 5%)\n```",
              "footer": "```scss\nsaturate($color, 5%)\ndesaturate($color, 5%)\ngrayscale($color)\n```\n```scss\nadjust-hue($color, 15deg)\ncomplement($color)    // like adjust-hue(_, 180deg)\ninvert($color)\n```\n```scss\nfade-in($color, .5)   // aka opacify()\nfade-out($color, .5)  // aka transparentize()\nrgba($color, .5)      // sets alpha to .5\n```",
              "spanConfig": "",
              "isShortcutsCard": false
            }
          ],
          "subsections": []
        },
        {
          "title": "Getting individual values",
          "level": 3,
          "cards": [
            {
              "title": "Getting individual values",
              "body": "",
              "footer": "#### HSLA\n\n```scss\nhue($color)         // 0deg..360deg\nsaturation($color)  // 0%..100%\nlightness($color)   // 0%..100%\nalpha($color)       // 0..1 (aka opacity())\n```\n\n#### RGB\n\n```scss\nred($color)         // 0..255\ngreen($color)\nblue($color)\n```\n\nSee: [hue()](http://sass-lang.com/documentation/Sass/Script/Functions.html#hue-instance_method),\n[red()](http://sass-lang.com/documentation/Sass/Script/Functions.html#red-instance_method)",
              "spanConfig": "",
              "isShortcutsCard": false
            }
          ],
          "subsections": []
        },
        {
          "title": "Adjustments",
          "level": 3,
          "cards": [
            {
              "title": "Adjustments",
              "body": "```scss\n// Changes by fixed amounts\nadjust-color($color, $blue: 5)\nadjust-color($color, $lightness: -30%) // darken(_, 30%)\nadjust-color($color, $alpha: -0.4)     // fade-out(_, .4)\nadjust-color($color, $hue: 30deg)      // adjust-hue(_, 15deg)\n```",
              "footer": "```scss\n// Changes via percentage\nscale-color($color, $lightness: 50%)\n```\n```scss\n// Changes one property completely\nchange-color($color, $hue: 180deg)\nchange-color($color, $blue: 250)\n```\nSupported: `$red`, `$green`, `$blue`, `$hue`, `$saturation`, `$lightness`, `$alpha`",
              "spanConfig": "",
              "isShortcutsCard": false
            }
          ],
          "subsections": []
        }
      ]
